reviewText: This was the worse movie I've seen in years.  I suffered through it just because I was hoping that it would get better.  I agree with other reviewers that the acting was terrible.  I wasted $1.99 to watch this movie.  Don't think about buying it or renting it, even if it goes on Prime
I really enjoyed this movie it was much more suspenseful than anticipated. I definitely recommend this movie!

It's an amazing movie telling the story of a very famous place called Casa Matusita in Lima Peru. Very scary place, that many people tried to expend a night in that haunted house, but no one can explain the very weird events that happened there. There are many versions of the Casa Matusita true, but Let me out Story, is the one that I like the most.
I Love it. Excellent effects, Thank You.
